func:
//let id = msg.payload["id"]
let asset_id = msg.payload["asset_id"]
//let portfolioname = msg.payload["portfolioname"]
let symbol = msg.payload["symbol"]
//let name = msg.payload["name"]
//let account = msg.payload["account"]
let exchange = msg.payload["exchange"]
let asset_class = msg.payload["asset_class"]
let asset_marginable = msg.payload["asset_marginable"]
let qty = msg.payload["qty"]
let avg_entry_price = msg.payload["avg_entry_price"]
let side = msg.payload["side"]
let market_value = msg.payload["market_value"]
let cost_basis = msg.payload["cost_basis"]
let unrealized_pl = msg.payload["unrealized_pl"]
let unrealized_plpc = msg.payload["unrealized_plpc"]
let unrealized_intraday_pl = msg.payload["unrealized_intraday_pl"]
let unrealized_intraday_plpc = msg.payload["unrealized_intraday_plpc"]
let current_price = msg.payload["current_price"]
let lastday_price = msg.payload["lastday_price"]
let change_today = msg.payload["change_today"]
let qty_available = msg.payload["qty_available"]
//let status = msg.payload["status"]
//let orderid = msg.payload["orderid"]

let sql = "INSERT INTO positions (account, asset_id, symbol, exchange, asset_class"
sql += ", asset_marginable, qty, avg_entry_price, side, market_value, cost_basis, unrealized_pl, unrealized_plpc"
sql += ", unrealized_intraday_pl, unrealized_intraday_plpc, current_price, lastday_price, change_today, qty_available) values "
sql += "('live', '" + asset_id + "','" + symbol + "','" + exchange + "','" + asset_class + "','" + asset_marginable + "','" + qty + "','" + avg_entry_price + "','" + side + "','" + market_value + "','" + cost_basis + "','" + unrealized_pl + "','" + unrealized_plpc + "','" + unrealized_intraday_pl + "','" + unrealized_intraday_plpc + "','" + current_price + "','" + lastday_price + "','" + change_today + "','" + qty_available + "');"
//node.warn(sql)
msg.query = sql
msg.market = market_value
msg.symbol = symbol
msg.gain_today = unrealized_intraday_pl
msg.gain_alltime = unrealized_pl
msg.pctgain_today = unrealized_intraday_plpc
msg.pctgain_alltime = unrealized_plpc
return msg;
